content.html: Growing up, #TDOV was always kinda tough. I wanted to be out so bad. The joy I felt when the few people I was out to wished me a happy TDOV made me feel truly seen. To all the trans kids unable to come out for now, happy #TDOV2023. This is your day as much as anyone else’s.
